Honestly, I don‚Äôt usually leave reviews but this place truly deserves one.

First of all, the villa and rooms are MUCH better than it looks in pictures. Extremely clean room and bed with exceptional attention to detail. You won‚Äôt find a stain anywhere, not even in the walls. It also feels luxurious and fashionable, blending rustic luxury with Bali‚Äôs essence.

Second, it has the best pool in Bali, with its water taken directly from the thermal natural pools in the volcano. It gets super hot and comfortable.

The location is perfect, super close to the volcano for trekking and other activities.

The most important part of this review is the hospitality and kindness of the owners. A family who completely takes care of everything with the best of their heart. They‚Äôll make sure everything is perfect. I don‚Äôt understand how just a family can have better service than 5 star hotels and the effort they put into making you have the best stance.

The dinner is fabulous as well.
